title: Brunch and Cake
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Mediterranean, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Brunch place that's frequented by a younger crowd. Vegan brunch entry is marked on menu: quinoa salad with roasted veggies, spinach leaves, roast corn on the cob, beetroot hummus with black sesame seed, and wholemeal bread. Blankets provided in cooler weather. Has Wi-Fi. No phone reservations.
